snippet: Clerical workers from a local office of the International Longshore and Warehouse Union on Tuesday night agreed to a new contract with terminal operators and will return to work Wednesday morning.
lead_paragraph: Clerical workers from a local office of the International Longshore and Warehouse Union on Tuesday night agreed to a new contract with terminal operators and will return to work Wednesday morning.
